title: Episode 20 ft. Boxer Andre Berto
itunes:title: Episode 20 ft. Boxer Andre Berto
description:
Andre Berto stopped by to see Angela Yee, Gigi Maguire and Stephanie Santiago after fighting Floyd Mayweather Jr and admits there is truth to why you should abstain from sex before fighting. He also talks about why he doesn't like messy sex and shares a memory of one of his best nuts ever.
